   <div class="contain">
    <div class="top-section">
    <h1> How to became a Social Media Influencer</h1>
    <p>
        Choose a niche , decide on the area that you are passionate about or have expertise in. It can be anything from fashion, beauty, technology, cooking, or fitness.

    </p>
    </div> 
     <div class="timeline">
        <div class="line"></div>
        <div class="section">
            <div class="bead"></div>
            <div class="content">
                <h2>Create a channel</h2>
                <p>
                    Create a YouTube channel or set up profiles on social media platforms like Instagram, Twitter, and Facebook.

                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="section">
            <div class="bead"></div>
            <div class="content">
              <h2> Develop engaging content
                </h2>
                <p>
                    Create content that is engaging, informative, and entertaining. Use high-quality visuals, clear audio, and creative editing techniques to make your content stand out.


                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="section">
            <div class="bead"></div>
            <div class="content">
                <h2>Build your audience</h2>
                <p>
                    Share your content on your social media profiles, collaborate with other creators, participate in online communities, and engage with your audience to build your following.


                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="section">
            <div class="bead"></div>
            <div class="content">
                <h2>Monetize your content
                </h2>
                <p>
                    Once you have a substantial following, you can monetize your content through sponsorships, brand deals, ads, merchandise sales, and affiliate marketing.


                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="section">
            <div class="bead"></div>
            <div class="content">
                <h2>
                    Stay consistent
                </h2>
                <p>
                    Consistency is key in building a successful career as a social media influencer or YouTuber. Post regularly, engage with your audience, and keep creating content that resonates with your followers.

                </p>
            </div>
        </div><div class="section">
            <div class="bead"></div>
            <div class="content">
                <h2>An overall journey
                </h2>
                <p>
                    Building a career as a social media influencer or YouTuber takes time and effort. It requires dedication, creativity, and a willingness to learn and adapt to changing trends


                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
      
     </div>
